sentences: Louise Viktoria Tolstoy (born 29 July 1974) is a Swedish jazz singer of Russian ancestry.
Tolstoy was a regular studio guest in season one of the television series Big Brother in 2000.
She was married to designer Per Holknekt from 2001 until they divorced in March 2008.
